headline: Trump-Branded Rent‑to‑Own Push and 55+ Expansion Might Change The Case For Investing In Lennar (LEN)
summary: Lennar was recently reported to be working with other major homebuilders on a large rent-to-own “Trump Homes” proposal that could channel private investor capital into as many as one million entry-level homes, while also opening its Dry Canyon 55-and-better community in Central Oregon with eight single-level designs starting in the low US$400,000s.
